title: The Cat & The Hat - Tricks & Treats.avi
description:
Just in time for Halloween, The Cat, Nick, Sally, Fish and the Things meet some new animal friends, including a coconut crab, spider monkeys and bats. In addition, there are some stories from Sid the Science Kid, Pocoyo, and WordWorld.

Rated TVY for all children. 

Genres:  Family, Kids  
Starring:  Martin Short, Jacob Ewaniuk, Alexa Torrington, Rob Tinkler, Tracey Hoyt  
Directors:  Tony Collingwood  
Studio:  NCircle Entertainment  
Format:  Fullscreen
